  "title": "Letter willing to comply with the request, made by Comdabra, to report UFOs in the brazilian airspace [1990]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/08/letter-willing-to-comply-with-the-request-made-by-comdabra-to-report-ufos-in-the-brazilian-airspace-1990/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1xb",
  "content": "<p><strong>FEB 14th, 1990. </strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>From: VARIG &#8211; Rio de Janeiro, February 14, 1990.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n<strong>To</strong>: Brigadier [&#8230;]<br />\nCommander of NUCOMDABRA<br />\nMinistry of Aeronautics<br />\nBrasilia DF</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em>Dear sir:</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n<em>We acknowledge receipt of your Official Letter 097 / CMD0 / C-201, dated December 26, 1989, which we are grateful for your attention.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em>We inform that we will attend to your request, when there is any report on Unidentified Flying Objects (UFOs), which may be observed in our airspace, by company airmen.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em>No more for the moment.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em>Kind regards,</em><br />\n<em>[&#8230;] Director of Operations</em></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.281. “Carta dispondo-se a atender a solicitação feita pelo ofício Comdabra, de 26 de dezembro de 1989, acerca de objetos voadores não identificados porventura avistados pelas aeronaves da empresa</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>FEB 14th, 1990.  From: VARIG &#8211; Rio de Janeiro, February 14, 1990. To: Brigadier [&#8230;] Commander of NUCOMDABRA Ministry of Aeronautics Brasilia DF Dear sir: We acknowledge receipt of your Official Letter 097 / CMD0 / C-201, dated December 26, 1989, which we are grateful for your attention. We inform that we will attend to [&hellip;]</p>\n",
